Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在笑着…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}预备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}预备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}身体好点了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 渐渐好点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}结果怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要恢复过来挺辛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哇 传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 我是短跑的松田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是跨栏的永井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是兵藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 我是雪哉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好了 柳 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嘿 居然都到互相叫名字的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}雪哉 别被妹子吸干了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}各位也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}积蓄太多是会影响成绩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前些时的烟火大会好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 我好想去看的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}明年一定要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.85,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那烟花放得很近的 好大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.08,Text,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然听不太懂不过好厉害的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说那种话没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}会有流言蜚语的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}让他们说去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我突然想起件事 先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}请问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}难不成小祐今天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去约会了 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冒昧问一句 他是在跟谁约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这我就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也不会那么清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你是叫透子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你最近也越发有女人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}夏日是恋爱的季节吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哎呀我真是的 怎么能对客人说这种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没事没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}作为赔礼 我请你吃曲奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过… 那…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}上次多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就为了这么一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}特地追得气喘吁吁的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}想跟你说几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你肯定做过这种事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}对着美术室里素描用的石膏像说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来整理自己的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没做过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子可是做过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我不答话也没问题是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 透子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 今天她要来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等等哦 我这就下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}大概是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 那我去打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一会再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪在高一的夏天时伤到了腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}现在在康复训练中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天还去参加了附近初高中合办的个人纪录赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过成绩不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}听说小祐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天去约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我还以为肯定是和小幸约会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是今天都说好了要来找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小幸 你在和小祐交往么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}他刚才还在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}感觉今天都是让我吃惊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过 真没想到你们俩都已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}进展到这般地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子 你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我没说我们在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天也只是一起在这里读书而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过如此而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒是透子 从那以后你还在跟那个人见面什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 是见过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}冲仓他虽然看着挺严肃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过多少也有他温柔的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}毕竟是个帅哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是这么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不是这么回事啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我最近要住几天院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只是住院检查而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}完全不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然后呢 出院以后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我有个想和透子一起去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸 哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还不能告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是能看见未来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}总觉得小雪现在很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过大家也都想知道未来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真的一句话都不想说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是 我是不会看的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 这里是冲仓家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 冲仓同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}能见下面么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有点事情想拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那天晚上你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我认真考虑过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 驱的话现在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呃 不好意思现在才跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是驱的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等他回来了我会告诉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸～！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我…我先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}说好了不要随便进来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这是什么书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}没什么没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}只是偶尔也想读读书而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你买的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你小子怎么可能会看加缪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}加缪啊加缪 还特么是薛西弗斯神话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}扯淡啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是那个红颜薄命的眼睛妹子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喂 我是深水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 不好意思刚才不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.99,0:12:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个 刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}老爸也说真是对不起那个小姑娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也要道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是我自己搞错了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}现在要来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是你有空的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}老爸想亲自下厨给你压压惊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}亲自下厨？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}老爸长年单身生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}厨艺不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你找我有事不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呃 虽然是有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也有件事一定要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}知道我家在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}呃 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我叫深水透子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 我来随便做点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就当是小点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}驱 你就先陪陪深水同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}毕竟她今天也算是我的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不要怠慢了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那首先 请去我的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我的房间在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前阵子 就是 下阵雨那天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在麒麟馆那条坡上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是不是我去抱高山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}而是扶住了她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}抱…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你知道她那天脚上有伤的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这件事到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}然后 她在坡上差点摔倒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 也不是什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过今天我找你来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也是因为高山的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}高山看起来要跟井美雪哉告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我是说 高山看起来要跟井美雪哉告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}什么 什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你怎么会连小柳的这种事情都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你看到未来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她本人告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还拜托我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:14:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这件事 想请你告诉透子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}理由是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}理由就不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}石膏像可不能说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}怎么样 驱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}趁这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你也办台手机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}会方便很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗 有那么方便吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}啊 确实是吧 没有手机说不定就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有人会跟我打电话么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小柳的脚已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}是吗 那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒是姐姐你啊 就因为男朋友在住院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就建构起这么强大的医院情报网了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}去了多少次医院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}一周三天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那是当然 我们简直就是天生一对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}毕竟他父母是带着孩子的再婚夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在那复杂的家庭环境里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们的心儿宛若秋风之中的一片树叶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}又好比风雨中的一叶扁舟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}尽受折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}够了 给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好朋友…之拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}真是承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}前阵子 找到了一个挺有意思的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}发现的时候 怎么都想要哪天带你去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要现在就去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}等我一下 马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天真是多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}相当美味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}拜托你跟你爸爸说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我这就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}透子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}还没跟我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}柳 你没回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}嗯 休息处
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}稍事休息 补充水与食物之类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}为接下来做准备的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你这不是没带水么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有点事情想跟小雪说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}喜欢小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我知道小雪喜欢透子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}也知道你已经跟她告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我也清楚要是被小雪拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就没法像再以前那样幸福地生活在同一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我们 就如小雪所说是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}小雪的回答我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}或许我该说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}要是小雪放弃透子选择我的话我会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但是你也会看不起我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}不过我还是要说出口来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}虽然我不知道我们的将来会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}但这里是 我今后的前进的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我想在此告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在家里拜托还像以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}今天听到了一句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}在车站擦肩而过的女高中生说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}她说啊 1221年是承久之乱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:19.48,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be2\an7\fs49.5\fad(300,300)}承久之乱是日本镰仓时代承久3年（1221年）\N后鸟羽上皇为打倒镰仓幕府举兵讨幕，\N却失败遭到镇压的兵乱。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}女高中生也真辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}阳菜 去拿筷子什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}姐姐 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}因为我想亲口说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}这种话 说明不了什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我真是个名副其实的大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我到底算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be2}来校园里 我们把话说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur12\3a&H99&\pos(960,727.5)}第6集 「拳头」
